Lagos – Lagos socialite, Pretty Mike turned heads after attending a friend’s wedding reception with five women dressed as brides. Pretty Mike has shocked wedding guests after he made an unusual appearance at a friend’s wedding reception. Pretty Mike was the cynosure of all eyes last Saturday, September 21st when he stormed a wedding reception accompanied by five models who were dressed as brides. The Lagos big boy is notorious for attending ceremonies in the weirdest fashion anyone can ever think of. Watch the video below: Source